* Standard Access Mode Libraries
** Requires allowlist for
***_ Maven coordinates
***_ JAR files
***_ Init scripts
** Allowlist managed by metastore admin
*** In Catalog Explorer
****_ Metastore settings
****_ Allowed JARs/Init Scripts
** Allowlist formats
***_ groupId:artifactId:version (exact)
***_ groupId:artifactId (all versions)
***_ groupId (all artifacts)
** Path allowlisting
***_ Prefix matching
***_ Include trailing slash
***_ e.g. /Volumes/prod-libraries/
** Allowlist ≠ data access
***_ Still need READ VOLUME permission
@endmindmap
